markets.title: What will MrBeast say during Next Youtube Video?
markets.rules_primary: If MrBeast says Tesla as part of Next Youtube Video, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: Video of the Next Youtube Video will be primarily used to resolve the market; if a consensus by Kalshi employees cannot be reached using video, transcripts of the Next Youtube Video will be used according to the news publications listed in the contract. The exact phrase/word, or a plural or possessive form of the phrase/word, must be used. Grammatical/tense inflections are otherwise not included. For the purposes of this market, “MrBeast’s next video” refers to the first full-length upload on MrBeast’s main YouTube channel (@MrBeast) after Aug 19, 2025 at 10:00 AM. The video must be at least four minutes long to qualify. YouTube Shorts, teaser trailers, live streams, community posts, and uploads on other channels (e.g., Beast Philanthropy, MrBeast Gaming, Beast Reacts) are excluded. Please see full rules for more details.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
